Torque Sockets

Top-level directory contents overview:

core:
	core foundation class library -- containers, basic types, etc.

lib:
	third-party utility libraries needed to build torque_sockets
	and the plugin.

license:
	source code licensing information.  TorqueSocket and
	torque_sockets are released under the MIT license
	See: http://www.opensource.org/licenses/mit-license.php

products:
	build products for the TorqueSocket family -- the torque_sockets c library,
	TorqueSocket plugin prototype and unit tests.

README:
	this file.

torque_sockets:
	c and c++ reference APIs and implementation.

TorqueSocket_API.txt:
	High level API specification for the TorqueSockets web plugin API